  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The intended use is limited to Class II spinal implant regulatory submissions under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending loading, evaluated against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories (FDA and DePuy Synthes), using Ansys Mechanical FEA. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed; Test conditions factor achieved below required level due to single test condition coverage. Model risk level 3 per ASME V&V 40 Table 2.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-static-compression-bending",
